The tracking number for your order is: {{9.mappable_column_values.text654}} and it was sent via {{9.mappable_column_values.dropdown0.text}}. It was sent to the address with postal code {{9.mappable_column_values.text71}} and should be arriving with you shortly. 

Your order can be tracked via the mail carrier's websites, let me know if you aren't able to find them and I can provide you with a link. 

Thanks {{9.mappable_column_values.text65}}, we appreciate the business, and please let us know what you think of your product once it arrives.

notes.content:
Changes to Make

1. Add Airtable Search to find Vendor Contact and Address in Embroidery & Print Airtable Boards.

2. Reformat ship request to book label with vendor shipping from address

3. Use Email and name indicated in Airtable document to email shipping label to vendor.

4. Remove all print steps.

5. Book Pickup for same day prior to 5 pm if west coast pacific time, 5 pm in eastern time if East Coast Vendor

6. If nothing found in first airtable board for embroidery - search one for screenprinting

View for Screenprinting Airtable: https://airtable.com/appiphQbZyJ9dzFrG/shrcpReyYAWAQPeYk

View for Embroidery: https://airtable.com/appUFCIi9Za8DMJ4s/shrKoGGK3MN5eOAaj
